 by gm the company ranked at  on the fortune  acquisition by general motorsedit in july  general motors entered into a definitive agreement to acquire americredit in an allcash transaction valued at approximately  billion the deal provided gm with a new financial arm to replace the loss of gmac now ally financial in  following the approval of the deal by americredit shareholders gm renamed the company gm financial on oct   on sept   gm and gm financial announced they entered into a support agreement providing for leverage limits and liquidity support to gm financial if needed as well as other general terms of support under the terms of the agreement as gm financial expands its product portfolio and grows its business gm committed to provide funding to gm financial if its earning assets leverage ratio rises above predetermined thresholds gm extended an intercompany revolving credit facility to gm financial to provide up to  billion of liquidity if needed this facility which is subordinate to gm financial’s senior unsecured and secured debt will replace an existing  million line of credit from gm the agreement also provides that gm will use its commercially reasonable efforts to ensure that gm financial will continue to be designated as a subsidiary borrower on up to  billion of gm’s corporate revolving line of credit since being acquired by gm in  gm financial has significantly increased its share of gm’s business which now represents  percent of gm financial’s consumer loan and lease originations on sept   standard  poors ratings services upgraded the credit ratings of both gm and gm financial to investment grade with a stable outlook the new gm corporate and gm financial credit rating is bbb on june   fitch ratings upgraded the credit ratings of both gm and gm financial with a stable outlook the new gm corporate and gm financial credit rating is bbb international operationsedit in april  gm financial acquired financialinx one of the largest independent leasing companies in canada to expand product offerings into canada financialinx operates as a subsidiary of gm financial in november  gm financial announced the acquisition of ally financials international assets the transaction includes operations in austria belgium brazil chile colombia france germany greece italy mexico the netherlands peru portugal spain sweden switzerland and the united kingdom it also includes ally’s percent interest in its chinese joint venture gmacsaic motor the majority of those assets were closed in  with the remaining portion an equity interest in a joint venture in china completed jan   referencesedit  a b c d e  form k general motors financial company united states securities and exchange commission february     baker ahles  kaskovich june   after xto who are downtown fort worth’s biggest employers startelegram   fortune   top  american companies fortune  retrieved    gm to acquire americredit pr newswire   shareholders ok sale of americredit to gm the detroit news   a b gm and gm financial enter into support agreement gm media   sp upgrades gm and gm financial to investment grade gm media   fitch upgrades gms and gm financials idrs to bbb outlook stable   gm financial to acquire financialinx corporation reuters   ally financial posts profit on tax benefit reuters   gm financial completes purchase of international operations joint venture in china from ally financial wwwgmfinancialcom retrieved   v t e general motors divisions and subsidiaries vehicle brands buick cadillac chevrolet gmc holden holden special vehicles services acdelco gm certified service gm financial maven onstar geographic general motors canada cami automotive general motors de mexico general motors do brasil general motors egypt general motors india chevrolet sales india private limited general motors south africa general motors japan shareholdings fawgm  gmavtovaz  gm korea  chevrolet europe gm vietnam gm uzbekistan  uzdaewooavto  hrl laboratories  saicgm  saicgmwuling  baojun 