edit brands for the customers who have limited access to automobile financing through banks and credit unions the company also provides commercial lending products such as wholesale or floorplan financing to new and used vehicle inventory and dealer loans to finance parts and accessories as well as improvements to dealership facilities to provide working capital and to purchase and finance dealership real estate in addition general motors financial company inc provides automobile financing solutions in north america and internationally it offers prime and subprime lending and full credit spectrum leasing through franchised and independent dealers under the gm financial and americredit brands for the customers who have limited access to automobile financing through banks and credit unions the company also provides commercial lending products such as wholesale or floorplan financing to new and used vehicle inventory and dealer loans to finance parts and accessories as well as improvements to dealership facilities to provide working capital and to purchase and finance dealership real estate in addition it offers finance andor carrelated insurance products such as payment protection gap extended warranty and motor insurance through third parties and financing for fleets and storage centers as well as customer services the company was founded in  and is headquartered in fort worth texas general motors financial company inc is a subsidiary of general motors company detailed description  cherry streetsuite fort worth tx united statesfounded in  employees phone  fax  wwwgmfinancialcom key executives for general motors financial company inc mr daniel e berce chief executive officer president and director age  mr chris a choate chief financial officer and executive vice president age  mr michael s kanarios chief operating officer of international operations and executive vice president age  mr david brinkman executive vice president of brazil chile  columbia and president of 